subject: Tennis
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Fourth-seeded Agnieszka Radwanska, 21st-seeded Sloane Stephens and 31st-seeded Kurumi Nara were ousted, but Williams had another impressive showing, overpowering Timea Bacsinszky.
